Description: A privacy-friendly search engine that prevents the tracking of your personal searches by the big search engine companies and others.
Headquarters Regions: Asia-Pacific (APAC), Western US
Full Description: "Keep your searches private with SearchLock: the anonymous, encrypted search engine and browser extension." It is our mission to make internet users feel secure and safe while searching the internet, ensuring privacy and protecting unwanted eyes from seeing and exploiting personal information. One of the most significant challenges to conducting business and personal activities online is maintaining security and privacy. Every time you log on to the Internet, there is a risk–no matter how small–of some unauthorized party gaining access to your sensitive personal information. If this information falls into the wrong hands, you could face a host of problems ranging from credit card fraud, online theft, or unauthorized data access. Since any and all of these problems could result in lasting financial, professional, and personnel issues, it is imperative to implement some means to prevent search data from being accessed by unauthorized parties in the first place.  One solution that may just eliminate the risk associated with search data access is SearchLock. An innovative software extension that works with all major browsers, SearchLock employs multiple processes that allow you to perform common web activities without leaving a trace. Furthermore, none of your personal information is made available to any party, whether it is your ISP, the search engine itself, or any other unknown third party organization or individual.  When you perform a search on Google or any of the major search engines, the search words or phrases you type into the search box is actually saved by the search engine. This is done in order to make subsequent searches faster and more efficient. Unfortunately, this could also result in the search words being associated with you and your other online activities. SearchLock prevents this from occurring by halting any attempt to track your search terms. Instead of sending the search data directly to the search engine, SearchLock reroutes them automatically and directs them to a privacy-safe results page instead. This enables you to get the results you want–just as if you had performed a typical search–with the main difference being the total security and privacy of your data. SearchLock also prevents your keystrokes from being logged by the search engines, your ISP, employer, or any other third party. Because most keystrokes are sent over the Internet without any form of encryption, it is a simple matter for anyone with the tools, knowledge, and capability to intercept the data and use them for illicit activity. SearchLock prevents this from happening by encrypting all keystroke data. And because SearchLock interfaces seamlessly with the browser, the process is virtually undetectable.  A number of search engine services–Google and Yahoo! in particular–also own and operate online social media services. This may result in searches and search results being linked to your online account. This process is officially used to enhance the web experience, but it may also result in unwanted marketing and advertising. With the use of SearchLock, all searches you make are totally disassociated from your account, so you are free to browse and search for anything without having to worry about anyone finding out about your activities.  Nowadays, it can be quite a challenge to keep sensitive personal and professional information secure. With SearchLock, you can keep your information safe while you enjoy a totally secure web experience.

Description: Truck Bed Liners and Protective Coatings
Headquarters Regions: Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: We have been leaders in this industry offering premium protection products to customers since 1996. We have also expanded our product line by offering window films (both automotive and commercial) as well as a wide range of DIY products. We offer an extensive selection of polyurethane based protective coatings including the XO2 System, High-Pressure Polyurea Systems, and Cartridge Systems. XO2 is acrylic-reinforced, aliphatic, aromatic polyurethane. It is a chemically engineered product that uses the best characteristics of polyurethane. This gives us incredible strength and when combined with our patented acrylic blend, with ease of application and UV stability.  We offer best quality Truck Bed Liners and Protective Coatings Systems that are developed over a 2 year period in the labs of major universities and independent chemists before being original and applied to the first truck bed. The major design criteria when creating the Scorpion System was that the delivery system be 100% reliable while maintaining cost efficiency.  Scorpion is a batch mix system and was chosen because it allows the applicator to infinitely adjust critical factors such as dry time, texture, and color  Batch mixing also allows the applicator to introduce a number of granular additives for various effects. We apply all coatings with minimal, cost effective equipment. Our huge product catalogue includes variety of Scorpion products like Headlight repair kits, XO2 kits, Tools, Cartridge Systems, High Pressure Systems, Special Formulations, various start-up packages and a line of XO2 products. Apart from truck bed liners and window films we also specialize in print services, DIY products, Marine coating solutions and OEM, commercial or industrial services.

Full Description: Modavanti is the destination for the new generation of socially conscious consumers, like ourselves, who are looking to find stylish and sustainable fashion that fits our values without compromising on quality or design. At Modavanti we believe sustainable fashion is personal. It’s about finding your style. It's about passion, not prescription.  Whether it's a certain designer, a specific look or a sustainability characteristic, at Modavanti you can search for what matters most to you. But what is sustainability and how does it translate to fashion? Broadly speaking, sustainable fashion is about considering people, planet and progress along with style. Sustainable fashion can be sexy, comfy and luxurious. It's a mindset, not a trend; a lifestyle rather than an experience. At Modavanti we have a three-pronged framework for sustainability: environmentally friendly, ethical sourcing and social good.  No longer do you have to choose between looking good and being environmentally and socially aware. At Modavanti our amazing designers ensure that you can look good, feel good and do good in what you wear. We’re committed to social enterprise and believe passionately that profit and progress should go hand-in-hand. We believe in the power of our generation to change the world through sustainable fashion, and hope that you will join us.

Description: Global Technology Associates, Inc. is a software product company designing and building firewalls and network security applications.
Headquarters Regions: East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Global Technology Associates designs and develops turn-key UTM firewall systems.   GTA is a privately held corporation located in Orlando, Florida and was founded in 1992.  The original focus for GTA was custom application software development.  Early work included network and security software for the nuclear power industry, virtual reality systems and custom computing hardware/software projects.   In 1994 GTA began focusing on the development of a commercial Internet firewall and later that year released the GFX-94 Internet Firewall system, a unique dual walled design consisting of turn-key firewall software and hardware components.   In 1996 GTA released the completely turn-key GNAT Box Firewall, which had a tiny footprint, with the entire system fitting on a single 3.5" floppy diskette.  The GNAT Box was marketed at a low price-point unheard of for commercial firewalls in 1996 with an aim to offer small businesses a network security option which hadn't existed before. In 1998 GTA released it first hardware appliance based on the GNAT Box software.  Since that time GTA has continued to develop it's turn-key firewall operating system GB-OS and now markets a line of firewall UTM appliances for the SME marketplace. GTA's products are distributed and sold world-wide.
Industry Groups: Information Technology, Messaging and Telecommunications, Privacy and Security, Software
